Class Flight

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nagarro.model.Flight
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Flight>

    public class Flight
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Flight>
    This class defines the design of a flight with attributes Airline Name,Flight Number,Flight Departure,Flight Arrival,Validity Date, Flight Time,Flight Duration, Flight Fare, Availability and its class.
